(133, 1, '2017-03-19 01:27:47', '2017-03-19 01:27:47', 'State of Wisconsin Dairy Resources\r\n\r\nWisconsin Department of Agriculture, Trade, and Consumer Protection. Covers many facets of the state\'s agricultural sector.\r\n\r\nGrow Wisconsin Dairy Team. Created to increase support for growing Wisconsin\'s dairy industry, the Grow Wisconsin Dairy Team is a joint venture between the Department of Agriculture, Trade and Consumer Protection, the Department of Commerce and the UW Center for Dairy Profitability.\r\n\r\nWisconsin Milk Marketing Board. WMMB is a non-profit organization funded by Wisconsin\'s dairy farm farmilies. Their goal is to increase the sale and consumption of Wisconsin milk and dairy products.\r\nUniversity of Wisconsin Links\r\n\r\nUniversity of Wisconsin Extension. Provides statewide access to university resources and research.\r\n\r\nCollege of Agricultural and Life Sciences, University of Wisconsin-Madison. Established in 1889, CALS carries out UW-Madison\'s mission as a land-grant public university through excellence in teaching, research and public outreach across 19 academic fields.\r\n\r\nAgricultural and Applied Economics Department. Research, teaching and outreach in agricultural and applied economics.', 'Links', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-19 01:27:47', '2017-03-19 01:27:47', '', 23, 'http://dairymarkets/index.php/2017/03/19/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(134, 1, '2017-03-19 02:06:38', '2017-03-19 02:06:38', '<h3>Links to Other Resources...</h3>\nThe internet is a vast resource of information about many topics. This is a non-exhaustive list of links which focus on dairy profitability in different ways. You can jump to various collections of links below:\n\n&nbsp;\n<h4>State of Wisconsin Dairy Resources</h4>\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href="http://datcp.wi.gov/" target="_blank">Wisconsin Department of Agriculture, Trade, and Consumer Protection.</a> Covers many facets of the state\'s agricultural sector.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href="http://datcp.wi.gov/Farms/Dairy_Farming/index.aspx" target="_blank">Grow Wisconsin Dairy Team.</a> Created to increase support for growing Wisconsin\'s dairy industry, the Grow Wisconsin Dairy Team is a joint venture between the Department of Agriculture, Trade and Consumer Protection, the Department of Commerce and the UW Center for Dairy Profitability.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr />\n\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href="http://www.wmmb.com/" target="_blank">Wisconsin Milk Marketing Board.</a> WMMB is a non-profit organization funded by Wisconsin\'s dairy farm farmilies. Their goal is to increase the sale and consumption of Wisconsin milk and dairy products.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>University of Wisconsin Links</h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href="http://www.uwex.edu/" target="_blank">University of Wisconsin Extension.</a> Provides statewide access to university resources and research.</li>\n 	<li><a href="http://www.cals.wisc.edu/" target="_blank">College of Agricultural and Life Sciences, University of Wisconsin-Madison.</a> Established in 1889, CALS carries out UW-Madison\'s mission as a land-grant public university through excellence in teaching, research and public outreach across 19 academic fields.</li>\n 	<li><a href="http://www.aae.wisc.edu/" target="_blank">Agricultural and Applied Economics Department.</a> Research, teaching and outreach in agricultural and applied economics.</li>\n</ul>', 'Links', '', 'inheri