(213, 1, '2017-03-19 13:35:23', '2017-03-19 13:35:23', '<h3>An Overview of Risk</h3>\r\n[embed]http://dairymarkets/resources/Risk1.ogv[/embed]\r\n<hr />\r\nThe Center\'s learning modules are available in a variety of formats. Some are meant to be used by an instructor for group delivery, and some are meant to be self-directed learning either on, or offline. They are presented below by subject matter.\r\n<h4>Risk Management</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Farm Succession Planning</li>\r\n 	<li>Benchmarking the Farm</li>\r\n 	<li>Record Keeping</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://dairymarkets.org/cdp/Programs/Spreadsheets/AmountFeedALL4.xls"><img class="alignleft wp-image-117" src="http://dairymarkets/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/PDF-150x150.png" alt="" width="39" height="39" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Risk Management Handbook</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis document will be used throughout the online video modules as a companion to the presentations. You should download and print this document before beginning the series.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://dairymarkets.org/cdp/Programs/Spreadsheets/BuildingRentalValueV2.xls"><img class="alignleft wp-image-93" src="http://dairymarkets/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Excel-150x150.png" alt="" width="39" height="39" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>An Overview of Risk</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis is the first module in the Risk Management series. In this video, you will learn about what risk is, what risk management is, and a process, or plan, for risk management. This module is about 25 minutes long.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://dairymarkets.org/cdp/Programs/Spreadsheets/BuildingRentalValueV2.xls"><img class="alignleft wp-image-93" src="http://dairymarkets/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Excel-150x150.png" alt="" width="39" height="39" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Internal Assessment</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis is the second module in the Risk Management series. In this video, you will learn about your personal risk attitude and personality and you will explore the risk bearing capacity of your business. This module is about 20 minutes long.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<a href="https://dairymarkets.org/cdp/Programs/Spreadsheets/BuildingRentalValueV2.xls"><img class="alignleft wp-image-93" src="http://dairymarkets/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Excel-150x150.png" alt="" width="39" height="39" /></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>External Assessment and Priority</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis is the third module in the Risk Management series. In this video, you will identify the sources of risk to your business and determine the impact to your business if that risk occurs. This module is about 15 minutes long.\r\n\r\n', 'Programs & Workshops', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-19 13:35:23', '2017-03-19 13:35:23', '', 18, 'http://dairymarkets/index.php/2017/03/19/18-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
